<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٢٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5651">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ سِنَانٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ عَبْدَ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنَ عَوْفٍ وَالزُّبَيْرَ: شَكَوَا إِلَى النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَعْنِي الْقَمْلَ فَأَرْخَصَ لَهُمَا فِي الْحَرِيرِ فَرَأَيْتُهُ عَلَيْهِمَا فِي غَزَاةٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>